com.supenta.flitchio.sdk

Class Status.FailingStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.supenta.flitchio.sdk.Status
      • com.supenta.flitchio.sdk.Status.FailingStatus
  • Enclosing class:
    Status

    public static class Status.FailingStatus
extends Status
    Subclass of Status describing that a failure has happened. A failing status has a Status.BINDING_FAILED code and it holds the reason of the failure in Status.failureReason.
    Since:
    0.7.0
